  "instructions": [
    "Heat the coconut oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until it is translucent.",
    "Add the ginger and garlic and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the curry powder and turmeric and cook for one minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the mackerel fillets and cook for 3-4 minutes on each side.",
    "Add the lemon juice, salt, and black pepper, and stir well.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Serve the curry hot, garnished with fresh cilantro or scallions."
